   167â†’### Un / Escape
   169â†’Turn the given string into a safe to  
   170â†’use key or value in your INI file.
   171â†’
   172â†’```js
   173â†’safe(`"unsafe string"`) // -> \"unsafe string\"
   174â†’```
   175â†’
   176â†’Or reverse the process with:
